# Absolute base URL for the VPN API, baked into the production build.
# The built panel at https://vpnadmin.mydayai.uz calls this URL directly
# (cross-origin), with CORS pinned server-side to the admin origin.
# Leave blank for `npm run dev` to go through the Vite proxy instead.
VITE_API_URL=https://vpnapi.mydayai.uz:9443
